<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Recent UCF MFA Grad Screens Film in Shanghai</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert and Tom Hurter
		
		<span class="date">June 18, 2009</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1799/en_US/actsofmercymain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Courtesy of ActsofMercyMovie.com </p>
			
			<p>Aleksa Palladino stars in a UCF graduate's film, "Acts of Mercy." </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041037381429012136c33d79005534">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
